::Shadow Wing::

She knew tha he could see her now.  But that didn't matter.  She was 
enjoying the moment.  She knew that they were supposed to be having a 
more physical fighting match between them.  But she knew that she was 
no match for him physically.  He was stronger than her pure and 
simple.  She wasn't build for fighting and she knew it.  So she had 
to out think him as opposed to trying to out mucsle him. 

She saw him run into the cave.  She swooped down and transformed into 
bot mode.  She kept her sachel on her shoulder and looked around.  He 
was inside the cave, but that didn't mean that she would follow him.

She climbed up to the roof of the cave and stood on top of the 
opening.  She layed down and hung her head down to 
yell. "HHHHHHHEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEELLLLLLLLLLOOOOOOOOOOOOOO  
IIIIINNNNNN THEEEEEEEEERRRRRRRREEEEEEEEE!"
She got up and jumpd back a few feet just incase he tried to grab her 
and pull her down.  She hoped he heard her well enough.
